                            <comment id="12642029" author="pkamath" created="Thu, 23 Oct 2008 01:04:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch to fix the issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;the earlier code was not catching the exception which hadoop throws when it tries to access a unauthorized directory. The fix catches this exception and bubbles it up as an IOException&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;All unit tests passed with the patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
